==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[W:International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]]:/bʌmp/

===Noun===
[[Category:English nouns]]
'''bump'''
# A light [[blow]] or jolting [[collision]].
# A [[protuberance]] on a level surface.
# A [[swell]]ing on the skin caused by illness or injury.
# ([[Rowing]]) The point, in a race in which boats are spaced apart at the start, at which a boat beings to overtake the boat ahead.

====Translations====
*Spanish: [[chichón]] {{m}}, [[bache]] {{m}}, [[abolladura]] {{f}}

===Verb===
[[Category:English verbs]]
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|bump||}}
# Knock or run into with a [[jolt]].

